div.p:
In negotiations just completed by Treasury and State, Japan agreed to a
                            package amounting to $350 million: 


                                    — increased purchases of time deposits in the U.S.
                                    $210 million;



                                    — increased military purchases and direct investments in
                                        the U.S. combined
                                    $100 million;



                                    — other
                                    $ 40 million




                                    $350 million
